# Copy to .env.local and adjust for your local dev setup.
#
# ---- Backend FastAPI URL ----
# Server-side forward (Next API route -> FastAPI) memprioritaskan
# `BACKEND_INTERNAL_URL`. Client-side (browser) memakai `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL`.
#
# Development:
#   Boleh kosong. Helper `getBackendUrl()` jatuh balik ke
#   DEV_BACKEND_URL (`http://127.0.0.1:8000`) yang hidup di
#   `frontend/src/app/lib/auth-cookie.ts` saat NODE_ENV != "production".
#
# Production / required:
#   WAJIB / required. Salah satu dari `BACKEND_INTERNAL_URL` atau
#   `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` harus ter-set; helper `getBackendUrl()` akan
#   `throw` kalau dua-duanya kosong di production runtime.
#
# Vercel staging:
#   BACKEND_INTERNAL_URL=https://insightsphere-api-staging.onrender.com
#   NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://insightsphere-api-staging.onrender.com
# Both values are required for production builds/runtime.
BACKEND_INTERNAL_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=http://127.0.0.1:8000

# Enable only when debugging React Query cache in the browser.
NEXT_PUBLIC_ENABLE_QUERY_DEVTOOLS=false
